        public static <T extends OverviewStats,V extends AbstractVersionDetails> T fromUpdates(Collection<V> updates,
                                                                                       ArtifactVersionsCache cache,
                                                                                       boolean allowSnapshots)
        Creates a OverviewStats instance based on the collection of version updates in the argument
        Type Parameters:
        T - subclass of OverviewStats
        V - subclass of ArtifactVersions
        Parameters:
        updates - collection of all version updates, typically from AbstractUpdatesModel.getAllUpdates()
        cache - if not null, cache to retrieve the version information, initialised with the AbstractVersionDetails.getNewestUpdateWithinSegment(Optional, boolean) update information
        allowSnapshots - whether snapshots should be included
        Returns:
        instance of the OverviewStats
